  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db1\u0dcf \u0dba\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc3 \u0d94\u0dc3\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Corona raises its head again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Director General of Health Services announced that 143 patients infected with 'Covid' were newly identified today (29).",
        "According to the report of the Director General of Health Services, the total number of 'Covid' patients reported in Sri Lanka is 665,543."
